         <ab>VVrS86.1 (mss. 4000, 4010, 4020, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161, 4162):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ēn gyāg <em>vīspaēibiiō sastīm baraiti</em> barsom az māhrōy abar griftan abar pāy estādan <em>ātarš mazdā̊ ahurahe</em>. ...</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At the passage, at <em>vīspaēibiiō sastīm baraiti</em>, he should take the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em> and stand (and continue with): <em>ātarš mazdā̊ ahurahe</em>. ..."</ab>
